{"tid":1762121,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[德國戰線］今個星期六日喺柏林會有手足搞喺德國第一次嘅義賣眾籌","createTime":"2019-11-29T11:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T05:07:23.000Z","uid":230840,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6602e1914ae83f7b77833e8e1ae5232993e00f57","tid":1762121,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dUgLLQ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdUgLLQ3.jpg&h=be1fd8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是咁的，今個禮拜六同日喺柏林有一個用亞洲做主題嘅聖誕市集，而喺柏林嘅手足靠住台灣朋友攞到其中一個攤位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以決定咗幫香港嘅手足搞喺德國第一次嘅義賣眾籌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅主題係雞蛋仔救香港，有個咁嘅主題又點可以冇熱辣辣又好味嘅雞蛋仔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，除此之外仲有台灣朋友整嘅酒釀丸子同柏林手足漏夜整嘅手製袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4Tuu3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4Tuu3X.jpg&h=984e0969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/events/671594023340482/?ti=as\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fevents%2F671594023340482%2F%3Fti%3Das&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbYwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=40b62f3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/events/671594023340482/?ti=as</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/events/2679826655430215/?ti=as\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fevents%2F2679826655430215%2F%3Fti%3Das&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbYwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=3bffa09b\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/events/2679826655430215/?ti=as</a><br />\n睇呢兩條facebook link有齊曬大會嘅時間同地址，如果住喺柏林又有興趣嘅朋友可以賞面過嚟食下嘢，吹個水都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，想藉呢個機會介紹下HongKongers in Germany Concern group呢個組織 ,佢哋有69果陣號慢慢集合德國各大城市既力量，連結同推動國內反送中遊行、示威、展覧、論壇、計埋協辦果d,大大少少既活動都有100個左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最出名嗰次，就係送咗幅集齊好多個簽名嘅banner返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而香港人在德國理事會（HongKongers in Deutschland e.V） 就喺十一月成立咗，以後HongKongers in Germany Concern Group 聯同出師有名嘅理事會一齊打好條德國線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然叫做香港人在德國，但組織成員唔單止係香港人，德國人、台灣人甚至中國人都有，共同嘅係大家都有一顆想幫香港嘅心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係組織嘅社交媒體，歡迎咁多位mon實我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFacebook:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/germanyswhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgermanyswhk%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbYwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=cae69ef0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/germanyswhk/</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/germany_with_hk?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgermany_with_hk%3Fs%3D09&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbYwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=02784f27\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/germany_with_hk?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\nIG(新開):<a href=\"https://instagram.com/stehthkbei?igshid=1mkc8us2pivrc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstehthkbei%3Figshid%3D1mkc8us2pivrc&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbYwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=cbe5b758\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/stehthkbei?igshid=1mkc8us2pivrc</a>"},{"pid":"857756e2da161aca2326004f25c34400d59f29f1","tid":1762121,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"自推10連（1/10）"},{"pid":"279c772fbe675